					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="5 Culture Truths Every Company Needs to Learn" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20150915181100-standing-up-in-office-.jpeg" rel="share" />

					
							
								
				
				
